  <brief_title>Does Vitamin D Improve Glycemic Control in Type II DM?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Vitamin D Improve Glycemic Control in Type II DM? A Double Blind Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
