  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Vitamin D status has been negatively associated with the presence of type II DM and glycemic
      control. However, a cause-effect relationship between vitamin D deficiency and glycemic
      control has not been established. The investigators plan to conduct a double blind,
      randomized, placebo controlled trial on the effect of vitamin D supplementation on glycemic
      control in Type II DM.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
